statements: SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE age_group = '18-24';
SELECT id, population, ethnicity FROM demographic_data WHERE region_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE income > 50000 ORDER BY age_group ASC;
SELECT id, region_id, age_group, income FROM demographic_data WHERE ethnicity = 'Caucasian' ORDER BY income DESC;
SELECT AVG(income) AS average_income, AVG(population) AS average_population FROM demographic_data WHERE region_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001';
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE region_id = '12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc' AND age_group = '18-25';
SELECT id, population FROM demographic_data WHERE ethnicity = 'White' ORDER BY population DESC;
SELECT region_id, COUNT(*) AS total_population FROM demographic_data GROUP BY region_id;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE income > 50000 AND (age_group = '26-35' OR age_group = '36-45') ORDER BY income ASC;
SELECT ethnicity, AVG(income) AS average_income FROM demographic_data GROUP BY ethnicity;
SELECT * FROM Districts;
SELECT district_name, population FROM Districts WHERE district_id = 1;
SELECT voter_name, age, gender FROM Voters WHERE age > 25;
SELECT district_name, demographic_data->'ethnicity' AS ethnicity FROM Districts WHERE district_id = 2;
SELECT voter_name, gender FROM Voters ORDER BY age DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM Districts WHERE district_id = 1;
SELECT district_name, population FROM Districts WHERE population > 50000;
SELECT voter_name, age, gender FROM Voters WHERE age >= 18 AND gender = 'Female';
SELECT district_name, population, demographic_data FROM Districts ORDER BY population DESC;
SELECT v.voter_name, d.district_name FROM Voters v INNER JOIN Districts d ON v.district_id = d.district_id;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data;
SELECT id, age, gender FROM demographic_data ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT race, gender FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 30;
SELECT representative_name, party_affiliation FROM representation_data WHERE party_affiliation = 'Democrat';
SELECT district_name, total_population FROM district_data ORDER BY total_population DESC;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 30 AND race = 'White';
SELECT district_name, total_population FROM district_data ORDER BY total_population DESC;
SELECT representative_name, party_affiliation FROM representation_data WHERE district_id = 3;

SELECT demographic_data.age, district_data.district_name FROM demographic_data INNER JOIN district_data ON demographic_data.id = district_data.demographic_data_id WHERE demographic_data.ethnicity = 'Hispanic';
SELECT * FROM representation_data WHERE party_affiliation IN ('Democratic', 'Republican') AND representative_name LIKE '%son';
SELECT state, city, population FROM Redistricting_Demographics;
SELECT ethnicity, age_group FROM Redistricting_Demographics WHERE state = 'California';
SELECT state, city, median_income FROM Census_Data ORDER BY median_income DESC;
SELECT * FROM Voter_Information WHERE party_affiliation = 'Republican' AND precinct_id = 12345;
SELECT representative_name, political_party, contact_email FROM District_Representatives WHERE district_id = 7;
SELECT state, city, population FROM Redistricting_Demographics WHERE population > 10000 ORDER BY state, city DESC;
SELECT state, city, ethnicity, age_group FROM Redistricting_Demographics WHERE state = 'California' AND age_group = '18-30' ORDER BY age_group ASC;
SELECT state, city, median_income, education_level FROM Census_Data WHERE education_level LIKE 'Bachelor%' ORDER BY median_income DESC, state ASC;
SELECT voter_id, state, city, party_affiliation FROM Voter_Information WHERE party_affiliation = 'Independent' ORDER BY state, voter_id DESC;

SELECT state, city, district_id, representative_name, political_party FROM Redistricting_Demographics RD JOIN District_Representatives DR ON RD.city = DR.city AND RD.state = DR.state WHERE political_party = 'Republican' ORDER BY state ASC, city DESC;
SELECT * FROM Districts;
SELECT name, population FROM Districts WHERE id = 1;
SELECT name, age FROM Voters WHERE age >= 18;
SELECT DISTINCT district_id FROM Precincts ORDER BY district_id DESC;
SELECT name, ethnicity FROM Voters, Ethnicity WHERE Voters.id = Ethnicity.voter_id;
SELECT * FROM Districts;
SELECT name, population FROM Districts WHERE population > 50000 ORDER BY population DESC;
SELECT d.name AS district_name, COUNT(p.id) AS precinct_count FROM Districts d LEFT JOIN Precincts p ON d.id = p.district_id GROUP BY d.name;
SELECT v.name AS voter_name, v.age, e.ethnicity, i.income FROM Voters v LEFT JOIN Ethnicity e ON v.id = e.voter_id LEFT JOIN Income i ON v.id = i.voter_id WHERE v.age >= 18 AND i.income > 50000;
SELECT v.name AS voter_name, d.name AS district_name FROM Voters v JOIN Precincts p ON v.precinct_id = p.id JOIN Districts d ON p.district_id = d.id WHERE d.population < 100000 ORDER BY v.name ASC;
